{"comments":"Session Storage — Configuration and types for session-scoped persistence.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nSession storage differs from local storage in lifecycle:\n- Local storage persists indefinitely\n- Session storage clears when the browser tab closes\n- Cookies have configurable TTL and cross-request semantics\n\nThis module provides a unified configuration for all three storage types,\nallowing agents to specify persistence requirements declaratively.\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nStorage configuration is pure data. Agents can reason about storage\nsemantics, compare configurations, and serialize storage intents\nwithout executing browser APIs.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Storage/Session.purs","start":[90,3]},"title":"LocalStorage"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[91,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Storage/Session.purs","start":[91,3]},"title":"SessionStorage"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[92,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Storage/Session.purs","start":[92,3]},"title":"Cookies"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Storage","Session"],"StorageType"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[94,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Storage/Session.purs","start":[94,1]},"title":"eqStorageType"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Storage","Session"],"Stora